\c 9
\s UJesu usilisa umuntu oyisigoga
\p
\v 1 Wasengena emkhunjini\x + Mark. 5.21. Luka 8.40.\x* wachapha wafika emzini wakibo\x + 4.13. Mark. 2.1.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Futhi khangela, baletha kuye umuntu owome umhlubulo elele ehlakeni\x + Mark. 2.3-12. Luka 5.18-26.\x*; uJesu ebona-ke ukholo lwabo wathi koyisigoga: Mana isibindi, ndodana; uthethelelwe izono zakho\x + Luka 5.20; 7.47,48. 1 Joha. 2.12.\x*.
\v 3 Njalo khangela, abanye bababhali bakhulumela ngaphakathi \add bathi\add*: Lo uyahlambaza.
\v 4 Njalo uJesu ebona imicabango yabo wathi: Lina linakanelani okubi enhliziyweni zenu\x + 12.25; 22.18. Mark. 2.8; 12.15. Luka 5.22; 6.8; 9.47; 11.17. Joha. 2.24,25; 16.19. Isam. 2.23. Hlab. 139.2. Seb. 1.24. 1 Lan. 28.9.\x*?
\v 5 Ngoba yikuphi okulula, ukuthi: Uthethelelwe izono zakho\x + Luka 5.20; 7.47,48. 1 Joha. 2.12.\x*; kumbe ukuthi: Sukuma uhambe?
\v 6 Kodwa ukuze lazi ukuthi iNdodana yomuntu ilamandla emhlabeni okuthethelela izono (wasesithi kowome umhlubulo): Sukuma uthathe uhlaka lwakho, uye endlini yakho.
\v 7 Wasesukuma waya endlini yakhe.
\v 8 Kwathi amaxuku esebonile, amangala, adumisa uNkulunkulu\x + 15.31.\x*, onike abantu amandla anje.
\s Ukubizwa kukaMathewu
\p
\v 9 Esedlula lapho uJesu wabona umuntu\x + Mark. 2.14-17. Luka 5.27-32.\x*, othiwa nguMathewu, ehlezi endlini yokuthelisela\x + 10.3. Mark. 3.18. Luka 6.15. Seb. 1.13. Mark. 2.14. Luka 5.27,29.\x*, wathi kuye: Ngilandela. Wasesukuma wamlandela.
\p
\v 10 Kwasekusithi ehlezi ekudleni endlini, khangela-ke, abathelisi abanengi lezoni beza bahlala ekudleni loJesu labafundi bakhe\x + Luka 15.1. Mat. 18.17.\x*.
\v 11 AbaFarisi sebebonile bathi kubafundi bakhe: Kungani umfundisi wenu esidla labathelisi lezoni\x + 11.19. Luka 15.2.\x*?
\v 12 Kwathi uJesu esizwa wathi kubo: Abaphilileyo kabadingi melaphi, kodwa abagulayo.
\v 13 Kodwa hambani lifunde ukuthi kutshoni\x + 12.7.\x* \add ukuthi\add*: Ngifuna isihawu, njalo hatshi umhlatshelo\x + Hos. 6.6. Mika 6.6-8. Mat. 23.23.\x*; ngoba angizanga ukubiza abalungileyo, kodwa izoni zize ekuphendukeni\x + 1 Tim. 1.15. Mat. 18.11.\x*.
\s Ukuzila ukudla
\p
\v 14 Khona kwafika kuye abafundi bakaJohane\x + Mark. 2.18-22. Luka 5.33-38.\x*, besithi: Kungani thina labaFarisi sizila ukudla kanengi, kodwa abafundi bakho bengazili ukudla\x + Luka 18.12.\x*?
\v 15 UJesu wasesithi kubo\x + Joha. 3.29.\x*: Abantwana\x + Ezra 2.1. Mat. 8.12. Luka 20.34,36.\x* bendlu yomthimba bangalila yini, selokhu umyeni elabo\x + 25.1.\x*? Kodwa zizafika insuku lapho umyeni ezasuswa kubo; khona-ke bezazila ukudla\x + 17.21.\x*.
\v 16 Futhi kakho obekela isichibi selembu elingakafinyeli\f + \fk elingakafinyeli: \ft kumbe, \fq ilembu elingakalungiswa\f* esembathweni esidala; ngoba lokho okubekelwe kuso kuzadabuka esembathweni, besesiqhela isikhala.
\v 17 Njalo kabatheli iwayini elitsha emigodleni emidala; uba-ke kungenjalo imigodla iyadabuka, lewayini lichitheke, lemigodla yonakale; kodwa iwayini elitsha balifaka emigodleni emitsha, besekulondolozeka kokubili\x + Jobe 32.19. Josh. 9.4. Hlab. 119.83.\x*.
\s Indodakazi kaJayirosi ivuswa ekufeni. Owesifazana owayelomopho uyasiliswa
\p
\v 18 Kwathi esakhuluma lezizinto kubo\x + Mark. 5.22-43. Luka 8.41-56.\x*, khangela, kwafika umphathi othile waguqa phambi kwakhe, wathi: Indodakazi yami isanda ukufa; kodwa woza ubeke isandla sakho phezu kwayo, njalo izaphila\x + 8.2.\x*.
\v 19 Wasesukuma uJesu wamlandela, labafundi bakhe.
\p
\v 20 Njalo khangela, owesifazana owayelomopho okweminyaka elitshumi lambili\x + Levi 15.25.\x*, weza ngemuva kwakhe, wathinta umphetho wesembatho sakhe.
\v 21 Ngoba wathi ngaphakathi kwakhe: Aluba ngithinta nje isembatho sakhe, ngizasindiswa\x + 14.36; 23.5.\x*.
\v 22 Kodwa uJesu etshibilika embona, wathi: Mana isibindi, ndodakazi; ukholo lwakho lukusindisile. Owesifazana wasesila kusukela ngalelohola\x + 9.2.\x*.
\p
\v 23 UJesu wasefika endlini yomphathi, wabona abakhalisa imihlanga lexuku liphithizela\x + Isam. 18.22. 2 Lan. 35.25.\x*,
\v 24 wathi kubo: Dedani; ngoba intombazana kayifanga\x + Seb. 20.10.\x*, kodwa ilele. Basebemhleka usulu\x + Joha. 11.11.\x*.
\v 25 Kodwa ixuku selikhutshiwe, wangena wabamba isandla sayo, intombazana yasivuka.
\v 26 Indumela yalokho yasiphumela kulelolizwe lonke\x + Seb. 9.40.\x*.
\s UJesu uhawukela iziphofu lesimungulu labakhathazekileyo
\p
\v 27 Kwathi uJesu esedlula lapho, iziphofu ezimbili zamlandela, zimemeza zisithi\x + 20.30-34.\x*: Sihawukele, Ndodana kaDavida\x + 15.22; 20.30,31. Mark. 10.47,48. Luka 18.38,39. Mat. 1.1. Hlab. 110. 1 Mat. 12.23; 21.9,15; 22.45.\x*!
\v 28 Esengenile endlini, iziphofu zeza kuye; uJesu wasesithi kuzo: Liyakholwa yini ukuthi ngingakwenza lokhu\x + 9.2.\x*? Zathi kuye: Yebo, Nkosi.
\v 29 Wasethinta amehlo azo\x + 20.34.\x*, wathi: Akwenzeke kini njengokholo lwenu\x + 9.2.\x*.
\v 30 Asevulwa amehlo azo; uJesu wasezilayisisa kakhulu wathi\x + Mark. 1.43. Joha. 11.33.\x*: Qaphelani, kakungabi lamuntu okwaziyo\x + 8.4.\x*.
\v 31 Kodwa zaphuma\x + Mark. 7.36.\x* zafakaza ngaye kulo lonke lelolizwe\x + Mark. 1.45.\x*.
\p
\v 32 Kwathi ekuphumeni kwazo, khangela, baletha kuye umuntu oyisimungulu\x + Luka 11.14,15. Mat. 12.22,24.\x* owayengenwe lidimoni;
\v 33 kwathi idimoni selikhutshiwe, isimungulu sakhuluma; amaxuku asemangala, athi: Kakuzanga kubonwe okunje koIsrayeli\x + 4.24.\x*.
\v 34 Kodwa abaFarisi bathi: Ukhupha amadimoni ngenkosi yamadimoni\x + Mark. 3.22.\x*.
\p
\v 35 UJesu wasebhoda emizini yonke lemizaneni\x + Mark. 6.6. Luka 13.22.\x*, efundisa emasinagogeni abo\x + 4.23.\x*, etshumayela ivangeli lombuso,\x + 4.23.\x* eselapha sonke isifo lobuthakathaka bonke ebantwini\x + 4.23.\x*.
\v 36 Kwathi ebona amaxuku, waba lesihelo ngawo\x + Mark. 6.34. Mat. 14.14.\x*, ngoba ayekhathele ehlakazekile njengezimvu ezingelamelusi\x + Isa. 53.6. Hez. 34.5. 1 Pet. 2.25. Nani 27.17.\x*.
\v 37 Wasesithi kubafundi bakhe: Isibili isivuno sikhulu, kodwa izisebenzi zinlutshwana\x + Luka 10.2. Joha. 4.35.\x*;
\v 38 ngakho ncengani iNkosi yesivuno\x + 2 Thes. 3.1.\x*, ukuze ithume izisebenzi esivunweni sayo\x + Mark. 1.12,43. Joha. 10.4.\x*.